### Use a extensão REST Client (VS Code) ou copie os comandos curl equivalentes

@host = http://localhost:5001

### Health check
GET {{host}}/health

### Registrar usuário
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### Login
# @name login
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "alice",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### Me (token vem do login acima)
GET {{host}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

### Listar usuários (excluindo o próprio)
GET {{host}}/api/auth/users
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
